   Markup/copy verbatim from reference/about-raw.html (cleaned of WP-Rocket
   lazy-load placeholders → reference/_about-body.html); section CSS lifted
   verbatim from the live page's inlined used-CSS (reference/_about-sections.css).
   Sections in DOM order:
     1. title-bar   — "About Phil Reese" H1 band
     2. phil-sctn   — portrait + intro
     3. philo-sctn  — My Philosophy
     4. yrs-sctn    — 20 years experience + stat boxes + medals
     5. sold-sctn   — Some of the Businesses I have sold (3 cols)
     6. social-sctn — Videos with Phil (12 lite-youtube embeds)
     7. awards-sctn — Awards & Track Record + Industry Recognitions grid
     8. awards-grid — Year-by-year award timeline (2 columns)
     9. background-experience-section — Licenses/Education/Experience/Publications
    10. ctc-sctn    — Contact form (CF7 field names → /api/contact)
   Notes:
   - The live site lazy-loads the 12 videos via wp-youtube-lyte; rebuilt here
     with the same lite-youtube web component the homepage uses.
   - Form reuses the homepage's field names + shared contact-form.ts handler.
   ----------------------------------------------------------------------- */
