<Layout
  title={pageTitle}
  description={pageDescription}
  canonical="/about/"
  ogImage={ogImage}
  ogImageAlt="About Phil Reese, Arizona Business Broker"
  ogImageWidth={1200}
  ogImageHeight={1200}
  structuredData={structuredData}
>
  <!-- lite-youtube web component — replaces the live wp-youtube-lyte embeds. -->
  <link
    slot="head"
    rel="stylesheet"
    href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/lite-youtube-embed@0.3.2/src/lite-yt-embed.css"
  />
  <script
    slot="head"
    is:inline
    src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/lite-youtube-embed@0.3.2/src/lite-yt-embed.js"
    defer></script>

  <!-- 1. title-bar -->
  <section class="section title-bar">
    <div class="section-wrap">
      <h1 class="maintitle h1-style">About Phil Reese</h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 2. phil-sctn -->
  <section class="section phil-sctn">
    <div class="section-wrap">
      <div class="img-col">
        <img
          fetchpriority="high"
          src="/images/about/MrPhil-1.png"
          alt=""
          width="417"
          height="588"
          class="alignnone size-full"
          srcset="/images/about/MrPhil-1.png 417w, /images/about/MrPhil-1-213x300.png 213w"
          sizes="(max-width: 417px) 100vw, 417px"
        />
      </div>
      <div class="txt-col">
        <p>Selling a business is one of the most important—and emotional—financial decisions an owner will ever make. I know that firsthand, because before I ever represented business owners, I was one. </p>
        <p>In 1995, my partner and I started First Impression Security Doors out of our garage in Mesa, Arizona. Over the years, we built it into a company that, at the time we sold it, operated out of our own manufacturing facility and had thirteen employees. Today that business is the largest ornamental iron company in the state of Arizona.</p>
        <p>We sold the company through a local Business Broker in 2001. My transition into the Business Broker industry came about when the President of the firm asked me to join his company. I accepted his offer and quickly became one of the top sales agents in the company.</p>
        <p>I am now affiliated with West USA and I focus on helping Arizona business owners sell their companies quietly, at the right time, and for the best possible price. West USA is the #1 Independently Owned Brokerage in Arizona and has one of the largest Business Broker groups in the state. The company was formed in 1986 and has 23 offices around the state, including 10 in the Phoenix metro area. This gives our businesses for sale listings excellent exposure.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 3. philo-sctn -->
  <section class="section philo-sctn">
    <div class="section-wrap">
      <div class="txt-col">
        <h3 class="maintitle h3-style">My Philosophy</h3>
        <p>I don’t chase listings—I focus on outcomes. I focus on quality, not quantity. Some business brokers will list any business regardless of the quality just to be able to brag that they have more listings than anyone. I turn down the majority of potential listings that come my way because I want to be able to spend the proper amount of time with each of my clients. It takes a lot of time and effort to get a deal done.</p>
        <p>I will give you a clear, honest assessment of value, timing, and expectations, even when it’s not what you hoped to hear.</p>
        <p>If you’re thinking about selling your business, the first step is understanding what you have and what your options are. That initial conversation is always confidential, no-pressure, and educational.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 4. yrs-sctn -->
  <section class="section yrs-sctn">
    <div class="section-wrap">
      <div class="one-col">
        <h3 class="maintitle h3-style">I have over 20 years’ experience helping people sell their businesses.</h3>
      </div>
      <div class="awards-inn">
        <div class="award-bx">
          <h4 class="subtitle h4-style"><span class="spn1">100+</span> <span class="spn2">Closed Transactions</span></h4>
        </div>
        <div class="award-bx award-bx-3">
          <h4 class="subtitle h4-style"><span class="spn1">$97M+</span> <span class="spn2">In Business Sales</span></h4>
        </div>
        <div class="award-bx award-bx-2">
          <h4 class="subtitle h4-style"><span class="spn1"><span class="spn1-inn">Master</span>CBI</span> <span class="spn2">1 Of Only 4 In The Entire State</span></h4>
        </div>
        <div class="award-bx award-bx-4">
          <h4 class="subtitle h4-style"><span class="spn1">#1</span> <span class="spn2">Top 1% West USA Realty</span></h4>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="medals-col">
        <div>
          <div class="medal-bx">
            <div><img src="/images/about/AZBBA.jpg" alt="" width="142" height="162" class="alignnone size-full" loading="lazy" /></div>
            <p>I am an active member of the Arizona Business Brokers Association, and I previously served as their Ethics Chairman. I took that role seriously because this industry only works when business owners can trust the business broker sitting across the table from them. That trust is something I’ve worked to earn with every client and every transaction for over twenty years.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="medal-bx">
            <div><img src="/images/about/IBBA-01-Vertical-2.png" alt="" width="180" height="164" class="alignnone size-full" loading="lazy" /></div>
            <p>I am an active member of the International Business Brokers Association. The IBBA is the organization behind the Master CBI designation, which I’m one of only four brokers in Arizona to hold. Earning it took years of closed transactions, advanced coursework, and a real commitment to the standards the IBBA sets for its members.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 5. sold-sctn -->
  <section class="section sold-sctn">
    <div class="section-wrap">
      <div class="title-col">
        <h3 class="maintitle h3-style">Some of the Businesses I have sold</h3>
      </div>
      {soldCols.map((col) => (
        <div class="sold-col">
          <h4 class="subtitle h4-style">{col.headline} <span>{col.type}</span></h4>
          <ul>
            {col.items.map((item) => <li>{item}</li>)}
          </ul>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 6. social-sctn — Videos with Phil -->
  <section class="section social-sctn">
    <div class="section-wrap">
      <div class="meet">
        <h4 class="subtitle h4-style sptmn">Videos with Phil</h4>
        {videos.map((v) => (
          <div class="vid-col">
            <div class="lyte-wrapper" style="width:853px;max-width:100%;margin:5px;">
              <lite-youtube
                videoid={v.id}
                title={v.title}
                style={`background-image:url('/images/about/yt-${v.id}.jpg');`}
              >
                <a href={`https://youtu.be/${v.id}`} class="lite-yt-fallback" rel="nofollow">Watch this video on YouTube</a>
              </lite-youtube>
            </div>
            <h4 class="h4-style vid-tle">{v.title}</h4>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 7. awards-sctn -->
  <section class="section awards-sctn">
    <div class="section-wrap">
      <div class="one-col">
        <h3 class="maintitle h3-style">AWARDS &amp; TRACK RECORD</h3>
        <p>Results matter, especially when selling a business. My approach to accurate valuation, disciplined buyer screening, and hands-on deal management has led to consistent recognition at both the local and national levels. Rather than listing every award since I began in 2001, below are highlights from my years with West USA Realty, home to one of the largest business brokerage groups in Arizona.</p>
        <h4 class="subtitle h4-style sptmn">By the Numbers</h4>
      </div>
      <div class="txtbox">
        <p><span>$97 Million +</span>
        In Closed Business Sale Transactions</p>
      </div>
      <div class="txtbox txtbox-2">
        <p><span>100 +</span>
        Businesses Successfully Sold</p>
      </div>
      <ul class="chklst">
        <li>Multiple years ranked Top 1% Overall Company-Wide</li>
        <li>Repeated Multi-Million Dollar Producer recognition</li>
        <li>Honors for Highest Sales Volume and Largest Single Transaction</li>
      </ul>
      <div class="one-col">
        <h3 class="maintitle h3-style">INDUSTRY RECOGNITIONS</h3>
        <hr />
      </div>
      <div class="awards-col">
        {awardImgs.map((img) => (
          <img src={`/images/about/${img.src}`} alt="" width={img.w} height={img.h} class="alignnone size-full" loading="lazy" />
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 8. awards-grid — Year-by-year award timeline -->
  <div class="awards-grid">
    <div class="awards-column">
      {awardColumnA.map((yr) => (
        <section class="year-section">
          <div class="year-header">
            <span class="year-number">{yr.year}</span>
            <div class="year-line"></div>
          </div>
          <ul class="award-list">
            {yr.items.map((it) => <li class="award-item">{it}</li>)}
          </ul>
        </section>
      ))}
    </div>
    <div class="awards-column">
      {awardColumnB.map((yr) => (
        <section class="year-section">
